data.description: Welcome to the Alma Farms subdivision! Don't miss your opportunity to own this beautifully maintained 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home with a fenced in backyard.  This spacious home has a large kitchen with abundant cabinet space, stainless steel appliances, and showcases a beautiful backsplash, plus a spacious floor plan with beautiful LVP flooring. The first floor also has a half bathroom and a seperate laundry room. Upstairs you'll find two guest bedrooms, a full bathroom and the gorgeous owners suite. The owners suite includes a walk-in closet, master bathroom with dual sinks, shower and separate garden tub as well as access to your own private balcony! This home is located in the back of the neighborhood on a cul de sac lot just minutes to shopping, restaurants, and the gate to Camp Lejeune. Call today to schedule a private showing! $1000 Agent Bonus if Under Contract by 2/9/2024
